## 7. 批量写入最佳实践

### 种子生成最优写入模式

```python
def init_db(db_path: str) -> sqlite3.Connection:
    """初始化种子数据库连接（写入优化配置）"""
    conn = sqlite3.connect(db_path, timeout=30)
    conn.execute("PRAGMA journal_mode=WAL")
    conn.execute("PRAGMA synchronous=NORMAL")
    conn.execute("PRAGMA cache_size=-65536")  # 64MB
    conn.execute("PRAGMA temp_store=MEMORY")
    return conn


def save_trades(conn: sqlite3.Connection, trades: list[tuple]) -> None:
    """批量写入交易记录（单事务）"""
    with conn:
        conn.executemany(
            "INSERT INTO paired_trades VALUES (?,?,?,?,?,?,?,?,?,?,?)",
            trades
        )
    # with 块结束自动 commit


def save_combo_summary(conn: sqlite3.Connection, summary: dict) -> None:
    """写入/更新 combo 汇总（upsert）"""
    with conn:
        conn.execute("""
            INSERT INTO combo_summary (strategy, coin, interval, total_return, total_trades)
            VALUES (:strategy, :coin, :interval, :total_return, :total_trades)
            ON CONFLICT (strategy, coin, interval) DO UPDATE SET
                total_return = excluded.total_return,
                total_trades = excluded.total_trades
        """, summary)
```

### 性能数据（实测参考）

| 配置 | 写入速度 | 说明 |
|------|---------|------|
| 默认（DELETE + FULL） | ~10,000 行/秒 | 每次 commit 等 fsync |
| WAL + NORMAL | ~250,000 行/秒 | 写入不阻塞读取 |
| WAL + OFF | ~400,000 行/秒 | 最快但断电风险 |
| executemany + 单事务 | 比逐条快 100x | 一次 fsync |

